display_long_description:
Have you ever looked at a panda and thought, “I want that life”?
Now you can. Be the Panda
Walk with panda arms, grab with paws, hold things with your mouth, and eat bamboo piece by piece. Your instincts decide how the world reacts.

👉 Important Note Before You Buy
I Am Panda is still incomplete. Not all features are ready yet.
Content will expand through updates as development continues.
Please purchase only if you are patient and want to support the journey.

#  Play as a Panda
See the world through panda eyes. Walk with your paws and feel the weight of your fluffy body.
[media]
#  Eat as a Panda
Eat bamboo piece by piece — or try to eat everything you find. Your mouth decides what’s food.
[media]
#  Cause Trouble as a Panda
Every object reacts to your actions. Grab it, hold it, throw it, smash it, Create chaos.
[media]
If you’re curious about the vision, want to give feedback, or just want to share silly panda memes — come hang out in the community:
👉 Join the Discord    https://discord.gg/2upDZSU2
